{"tid":1146580,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Apple Watch Series 4 榮獲「年度最佳顯示器」！","createTime":"2019-05-09T10:09:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-09T11:45:57.000Z","uid":109383,"like":5,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6706c565d801cd0a3fb35856622ecd42180ae362","tid":1146580,"uid":109383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T10:09:51.000Z","msg":"顯示器是我們與電子產品接觸的重要媒介，若是顯示器設計得好，甚至可以大幅提升使用體驗。而在今年資訊顯示學會 SID 的「年度最佳顯示器」獎項，就由 Apple 所推出的 Apple Watch Series 4 獲此殊榮。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twstatic.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Apple-Watch-Series-4.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwstatic.newmobilelife.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F05%2FApple-Watch-Series-4.jpg&d=oAUO7kpDmgkuxlfprI4EYbhWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=173a56ee\" target=\"_blank\">https://twstatic.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Apple-Watch-Series-4.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSID 表示該款產品在保留原本標誌性設計的同時，不僅變得更加優雅，還結合了硬體與軟體的改進，新的介面則提供更多的資訊與豐富細節。<br />\n<br />\n對設計者而言，最大的挑戰在於要製作出更大的螢幕，卻又不能明顯改變裝置的體積，亦不能對電量妥協。Apple Watch Series 4 除了以更窄的邊框完成這項挑戰之外，採用 LTPO 的顯示技術也可讓使用者光是充一次電即可滿足一天所需。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nApple又贏一杖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ae99b2e391b845dcd763f783b0e22bfd3785e65","tid":1146580,"uid":50658,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T10:21:17.000Z","msg":"負評係俾條link嘅"},{"pid":"e13a3747cb6b1404db4bb496df339ffc3568e49e","tid":1146580,"uid":109383,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0ae99b2e391b845dcd763f783b0e22bfd3785e65","tid":1146580,"uid":50658,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T10:21:17.000Z","msg":"負評係俾條link嘅"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T10:30:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/asse